class.name: GenericRecordBuilder
class.doc:
Bytecode generating GenericRecord builder.
Microbenchmarks show a 10% performance improvement. but depending on your data your performance benefits can be greater or smaller. The main benefit for this is the potential for eliminating the need for separate handling or generic records vs specific records in the avro lib...
